<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" />

    <style>
        .image {
            width: 50%;
            height: 40vh;
            background-size: cover; /* Ensures the image covers the entire div */
            background-position: center; /* Centers the image */
            color: white; /* Makes the text stand out on the background */
            padding: 50px; /* Adds space inside the div */
            text-align: center; /* Centers the text */
        }

        .custom-paragraph {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="row align-items-center my-5">
        <!-- Image Section -->
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
            <img src="/images/ContentCreation.jpg" alt="AI in Education" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Text Section -->
    <div class="row align-items-center my-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="p-4 bg-light rounded shadow-sm animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
                <h2 class="mb-3">AI In Education Tools</h2>
                <p class="custom-paragraph" style="line-height: 1.7; text-align: justify;">
                    Artificial Intelligence is revolutionizing education by enabling personalized learning,
                    automating administrative tasks, and enhancing student engagement. AI-powered tools adapt lessons to individual needs,
                    provide instant feedback, and support educators with smart content creation.
                </p>
                <p class="custom-paragraph" style="line-height: 1.7; text-align: justify;">
                    From intelligent tutoring systems to predictive analytics that identify at-risk students, AI helps improve learning outcomes
                    and streamline school operations. As AI continues to evolve, it offers innovative opportunities while also raising
                    ethical considerations such as data privacy and bias. When integrated thoughtfully, AI enhances education by
                    making learning more efficient, accessible, and engaging.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>